Life Domains. Most applications in the SWB literature appear to assume that the SWB
function aggregates consumption across life domains in the same way that the utility function
does: ğ‘¢Ìƒğ‘˜ (âˆ™) is assumed to be a positive affine transformation of ğ‘¢ğ‘˜ (âˆ™) (the same transformation
for all ğ‘˜ âˆˆ {0,1,2, â€¦ , ğ¾ }). This assumption is almost never explicit; an exception is Decancq,
