outliers, such as the â€œPurpose & meaningâ€ domain in the Meaning & Value question). Our
respondents thus report, on average, a similar domain weighting scheme across a wide range of
SWB questions. The domains â€œIncome & financial security,â€ â€œFamily life & relationships,â€

